<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer__inner">
    <div class="footer__brand">
      <span class="nav__mark" aria-hidden="true">◇</span>
      <span>TaskShip</span>
      <span class="footer__tag">Plan-as-code for Jira</span>
    </div>
    <nav class="footer__links" aria-label="Footer">
      <a href="#problem">Why</a>
      <a href="#how">How it works</a>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/selvakumarEsra/taskship">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://pypi.org/project/taskship/">PyPI</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="container footer__legal">
    <span>Built with Astro · Jira is the system of record, TaskShip is the system of intent.</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 44px 0 40px; background: var(--bg); }
  .footer__inner {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 18px; align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer__brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px; font-weight: 700; }
  .footer__brand .nav__mark { color: var(--brand); font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .footer__tag { font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink-faint); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-left: 6px; }
  .footer__links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; color: var(--ink-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .footer__links a:hover { color: var(--brand-ink); }
  .footer__legal { margin-top: 22px; color: var(--ink-faint); font-size: 0.85rem; }
</style>
